help:set types
                               set:  variable types


Boolean:              has only two allowed values true or false
                      set [no]<variable_name>  - sets the value
                      set [no]<variable_name>? - gets the value


Number:                            Python literal


Color:                     #<hex_red><hex_green><hex_blue>       | hex from 00 to ff
                                    <named_color>                |
Color with opacity:  #<hex_alpha><hex_red><hex_green><hex_blue>  | for named colors
                              <named_color_with_opacity>         | see :help python colors
